    public abstract class SetPeriodChart<P extends PeriodPlot>
extends PeriodChart<P>
    PeriodCharts that represent a set of values such as a pie-chart of bar-chart. Unlike TimeCharts only a single dataset is plotted. This defaults to the last created Plot but can be reset using the #setPlot(PeriodSetPlot) method.
